\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Well - the other sister was one, and she's two years younger than me, so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 So where did you move?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 To Cringles. Far
m. Cringles. Outside Silsden. Yes. Addingham. On the road - well - it's really between Silsden and Draughton, the little farm where I was born. See they called it Draughton Road. Where - not where I was born, where I went to live. Me other sister was born
 there. Oh wait a minute - three - I - I might not have been three, I might only have been - one. Yes. The other - I was thinking the other sister was one when we went but she was born up there. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 So you can't remember the house at Silsden at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Oh no. No I can't remember the house at Silsden at all. I can remember the house at Cringles. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 It was Cringles Farm?
