\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 And Draughton. Ye
s. Draughton. It's near Skipton. The road going over there. And that's strictly speaking because - if you were going to Addingham you could see this on the left. So that it's strict address would be Draughton Road. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 How long did you stay at Marchup Farm?
