Yes. I was - nearly five - when we left. So I think myself we'd be there about four years. I - I was just short of five when we went to live at Long Lee. Yes, we lived at Long Lee then, at Farthing Road. Mm. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 How long did you stay at Long Lee?
