\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Which would be quite rural at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 
Oh yes. Oh yes, there were - I - it's by - by the way but - I had to come back from Bradford Eye Hospital - less than a year ago, and - they'd taken
 me by ambulance because it might have been bad weather and I was old you see, so they brought me back by ambulance and we came over there. And - I could point out - all the houses that were there when I was there, and all the new - buildings - it's quite
 
different, but still I could spot them. I lived there and I remember that and I remember that. Oh it was most interesting to me was that ride. I rode outside with the driver incidentally, I asked him if I might, I was the last passenger, and I wanted if i
t was coming over Long Lee to see it you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 How long - you were at Long Lee, your father was working at Summer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 -}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 scales?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 And you left Long Lee when you were thirteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes.
