\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes, father still worked at Summer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
