 Mrs - yes, that's right, Mrs Nicholson, and - she's - 1898, I've heard her say it. - a few times recently. Seven and a bit you see younger than me. Isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 So she'd be six years younger than the one after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes. Yes. That's right. But - really about five and a half. Mm, because she's February and the other's November you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 What about your youngest sister?
