\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 
He was born in 1860. He must have been thirty. And his birthday was in December. Yes. And mother was four years younger. If you want hers. 1864. Also in November. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 When you were born must have been twenty-six?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 '64 - twenty-six, yes. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 You said he came from a farming family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Where was it he came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Old Silsden. Yes, yes, he was born in Silsden, yes. Mm.
