\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 He - it - it was - let me
 see - he was working in Keighley then, I think. Before he went up - up to Cringles. Yes, I don't think he ever worked at Steeton bobbin mill, he must have been - he must have been working in Keighley. I can't - he was - he must have been - because he had
 
an accident - and a circular saw - fell on his foot and - he was off work and of course they'd no money - soon after they were married, there was no - benefits of any kind, and - he was off work a long time and they were - in - difficulties, great - they 
h
ad to depend on - good friends and neighbours giving them even after food, for - during that time. When I was small, yes, I remember her tell about it you see, it was in Silsden where - and that was where I was born. We - we - it would be between the brot
h
er and me being born, it was in the very early married life. Or even before me brother was born. So then he - he would be working in Silsden to be where there was a circular saw, so I'm sure he never worked at - at Steeton and there was no other place. He
 didn't work in Silsden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 So he must have been travel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 ing to Keighley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Keighley, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 When you were born was he still working in Keighley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes. He would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 And then when you were about one or three you moved to Cringles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 One, I - you can safely say one, I made a mistake there. Went up there. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 You took this smallholding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes.
