\insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 scales - although part of it was on at Beechcliffe, they had a warehouse on there, but - he worked at Summer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
