\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes. When I was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Where did she come from?
