Oh - Annie, Mrs Green, she's younger than me. I'm next to me brother. Yes. We got the jobs tacked on to us as we got old enough. You see - it was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 So you all had to share them?
