cially the small children, if - if she was - getting us - she got them ready first, he would carry them up to bed. Whilst she got our supper. He - he's often carried smaller children, I pr}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 e}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 sume - he carried us only - I can't remember, but - he certainly carried the - younger children up to bed.
