 Me brother had - a small bed in the - narrow }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180  narrow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180  
