\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 No - buchess - bechese - ludo it's called now, it - it's the same game. Ludo. Ludo and dom}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7737737\charrsid15471180 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 noes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Did they ever play games outside with you, such as cricket or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Well - I don't think so. No, we went out to play with - we played whatever was going - with the other children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13525481 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 You've already said there were some books in the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Yes.
