\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5131904 OS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10517864\charrsid15471180 Mother had some books - that she bought - I think she bought them in sections and had them mounted, and they were - a gre
at deal to us were these books, and there were two of them, and - they were - they had every kind of animal, one had, birds and animals. The only thing that you couldn't judge size by the pictures, and I think they'd perhaps be alphabetically, I don't kno
w but - there were little pictures and an article about - every kind of animal and bird - that you could think - that we could think of at any rate.
